text: Eide og Omegn FK is a Norwegian association football club from Hustadvika, Møre og Romsdal. The club was founded in 1992, as a merge between Eide IL, Lyngstad IL and Frode IL. The men's football team currently resides in the Norwegian Fourth Division (Tier 5).
